summary: Full agent lifecycle via MCP server
description: |
    Tests complete agent lifecycle through MCP tools:
    registration, enrollment, status, policies, stop,
    reactivate, update, unenroll, and registrar removal.
    Runs with data masking enabled.
contact: Marek Safarik <msafarik@redhat.com>
component:
  - keylime-mcp
framework: shell
test: go test -v -tags=functional .
require:
  - golang
  - keylime
duration: 5m
enabled: true
